          "question": "Can my loved one work at SCSEP while receiving Social Security?",
          "answer": "Yes, SCSEP participants can receive Social Security benefits while working in the program. However, they must report SCSEP wages to Social Security, and earnings may affect benefit amounts depending on their age and Social Security status."
